      • registerCommand

        public void registerCommand(FussterPlugin plugin,
                            Command command,
                            java.lang.String label)
        Links a command to a plugin. When the plugin gets unloaded all the bound commands get unregistered. Also registers the plugin if the plugin isn't registered
        Parameters:
        plugin - The plugin that the command will be linked to
        command - The actual command to bound
        label - The label that the command should react to
        See Also:
